fixes #9895.

Although the address of RegistryConfig for MetadataService Config was set `N/A`, it gets overridden by the value set in `application.properties`. So we need to set the `register` property explicitly to false to stop it from being registered.

```java
 RegistryConfig registryConfig = new RegistryConfig("N/A");
registryConfig.setId("internal-metadata-registry");
serviceConfig.setRegistry(registryConfig);
serviceConfig.setRegister(false);
```
